 and JavaScript for better interaction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>For solution providers, from graphic designer to development team and   web consultant, FlexicaCMS helps to</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Turn a static HTML page into a dynamic page quickly </strong><br />By   replacing static content parts with simple FlexicaCMS tags</li>\r\n<li><strong>Easily present business information in special formats using   widgets</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Use unlimited page templates</strong><br />Content can be   displayed without any restriction of the page layout defined at the   early stage of the project and cannot cover special scenarios</li>\r\n<li><strong>Extend the system over time</strong><br />By adding new   modules to the CMS and creating new pages or editing existing page to   use the new widgets</li>\r\n<li><strong>Provide services and exchange data with other systems</strong><br />FlexicaCMS   uses SOA design, OOP coding technique and XML, JSON standards for data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\";s:5:\"Title\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"ShowTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"OverridePageTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"Wrapper\";s:29:\"<div class=\"Document\">|</div>\";s:11:\"ItemWrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"AllowCustomization\";s:1:\"1\";}',NULL,NULL),(25,14,'FEATURE_LIST','RichTextWidget','a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:991:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Totally visual customization on page<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Page tree and sitemap auto generation</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Category tree system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">System settings and module settings<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Reusable components<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Master layouts</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Customizable user roles system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Easily adding module and admin pages with a consistent navigation system<br /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Use MVC model, totally OOP code<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Error handling/reporting</a></