eating new pages or editing existing page to   use the new widgets</li>\r\n<li><strong>Provide services and exchange data with other systems</strong><br />FlexicaCMS   uses SOA design, OOP coding technique and XML, JSON standards for data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\";s:5:\"Title\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"ShowTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"OverridePageTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"Wrapper\";s:29:\"<div class=\"Document\">|</div>\";s:11:\"ItemWrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"AllowCustomization\";s:1:\"1\";}',305,'fr_fr'),(25,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:991:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Totally visual customization on page<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Page tree and sitemap auto generation</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Category tree system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">System settings and module settings<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Reusable components<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Master layouts</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Customizable user roles system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Easily adding module and admin pages with a consistent navigation system<br /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Use MVC model, totally OOP code<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Error handling/reporting</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Automatically server side input validation with XSS protection</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">SOA programming model</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Modular architecture with cross module service call</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Widget coordinator controller</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Customizable Role Base Access Control</a></li>\r\n</ul>\";}',306,'fr_fr'),(26,'a:11:{s:9:\"ShowIntro\";s:1:\"0\";s:10:\"CategoryId\";s:2:\"29\";s:12:\"DetailedPage\";s:2:\"15\";s:3:\"Top\";s:1:\"5\";s:11:\"ArticleType\";s:21:\"LIST_POPULAR_ARTICLES\";s:5:\"Title\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"ShowTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"OverridePageTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"Wrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"CssClass\";s:10:\"BulletList\";s:18:\"AllowCustomization\";s:1:\"1\";}',307,'fr_fr'),(27,'a:11:{