 on Yii framework. Very easy to learn, with a crowded supportive community.</li>\r\n</ul>\";}',424,'vi_vn'),(16,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:116:\"<p><strong>Easier content publishing<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Edit or customize content on page with visual editor</p>\";}',425,'vi_vn'),(17,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:108:\"<p><strong>Faster product to market</strong><br />Many ready to use modules and powerful developer tools</p>\";}',426,'vi_vn'),(18,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:99:\"<p><strong>More integration options</strong><br />Reusable components and Open API architecture</p>\";}',427,'vi_vn'),(19,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:495:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a title=\"Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry - Has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since thes, when an unknown printer.Simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\" href=\"#\">Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.</a></li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Dummy text - when an unknown printer.Simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\" href=\"#\">Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.</a></li>\r\n</ul>\";}',428,'vi_vn'),(20,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:495:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a title=\"Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry - Has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since thes, when an unknown printer.Simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\" href=\"#\">Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.</a></li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Dummy text - when an unknown printer.Simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\" href=\"#\">Dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.</a></li>\r\n</ul>\";}',429,'vi_vn'),(21,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:1094:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a title=\"Visual editors - Each sectiion on page is a widget that you can easily edit text content or its properties to show the right content in the right format you want.\" href=\"#\">Visual editors for all customizable page elements</a></li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Site structure and navigation system - The page tree is easily to manage with ability to drag-n-drop to reorder pages. Base on the page tree, you can create many menus with unlimited levels of pages.\" href=\"#\">Friendly site structure and navigation system</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a title=\"Reusable and customizable components - Everything is dynamic with a powerful parameter system. Modules and widgets are self-contained components that can be easily distribute or reuse in multiple projects.\" href=\"#\">Reusable, customization modules, components and services</a></li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Object oriented programming - Leverage Yii\'s application architecture and strictly OOP coded for ease of maintenance and improvement.\" href=\"#\">MVC, OOP, AJAX support and REST service readiness</a></li>\r\n</ul>\";}',430,'vi_vn'),(23,'a:14:{s:15:\"ShowPublishInfo\";s:1:\"0\";s:14:\"ShowCategories\";s:1:\"0\";s:10:\"ShowRating\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"ShowTags\";s:1:\"0\";s:12:\"ArticleAlias\";s:7:\"license\";s:10:\"AuthorPage\";s:1:\"0\";s:12:\"CategoryPage\";s:1:\"0\";s:10:\"SearchPage\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"Title\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"ShowTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"OverridePageTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"Wrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"ItemWrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"AllowCustomization\";s:1:\"1\";}',431,'vi_vn'),(24,'a:7:{s:7:\"Content\";s:1460:\"<div>\r\n<h2>Welcome to FlexicaCMS</h2>\r\n<p>The key features of FlexicaCMS are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Visualized content editing</strong><br />A new level of   WYSIWYG that let user to edit a page while viewing it. Formatting   content and enter the right content at the right place are no more the   concern</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enabled richer page content</strong><br />By combining   editable text and media with customizable structural data and present   them to users using CSS and JavaScript for better interaction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>For solution providers, from graphic designer to development team and   web consultant, FlexicaCMS helps to</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Turn a static HTML page into a dynamic page quickly </strong><br />By   replacing static content parts with simple FlexicaCMS tags</li>\r\n<li><strong>Easily present business information in special formats using   widgets</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Use unlimited page templates</strong><br />Content can be   displayed without any restriction of the page layout defined at the   early stage of the project and cannot cover special scenarios</li>\r\n<li><strong>Extend the system over time</strong><br />By adding new   modules to the CMS and creating new pages or editing existing page to   use the new widgets</li>\r\n<li><strong>Provide services and exchange data with other systems</strong><br />FlexicaCMS   uses SOA design, OOP coding technique and XML, JSON standards for data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\";s:5:\"Title\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"ShowTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"OverridePageTitle\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"Wrapper\";s:29:\"<div class=\"Document\">|</div>\";s:11:\"ItemWrapper\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"AllowCustomization\";s:1:\"1\";}',432,'vi_vn'),(25,'a:1:{s:7:\"Content\";s:991:\"<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Totally visual customization on page<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Page tree and sitemap auto generation</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Category tree system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">System settings and module settings<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Reusable components<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Master layouts</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Customizable user roles system</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Easily adding module and admin pages with a consistent navigation system<br /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list2\">\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Use MVC model, totally OOP code<br /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Error handling/reporting</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">Automatically server side input validation with XSS protection</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"\">SOA programming model</a><